---
// Privacy Policy Page
---

<section class="py-24 px-6 bg-background">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-[48px] font-bold font-serif text-secondary mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm mb-12">Last updated: January 2025</p>

    <div class="space-y-12">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-[24px] font-bold font-serif text-secondary mb-4">Introduction</h2>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
          Welcome to The Wedding Travel Company. We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal data.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-[24px] font-bold font-serif text-secondary mb-4">Information We Collect</h2>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
          We may collect, use, store and transfer different kinds of personal data about you.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-[24px] font-bold font-serif text-secondary mb-4">Contact Us</h2>
        <p class="text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed mb-4">
          If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us:
        </p>
        <ul class="text-muted-foreground space-y-2">
          <li>By email: <a href="mailto:privacy@weddingtravelcompany.com" class="text-primary hover:underline">privacy@weddingtravelcompany.com</a></li>
          <li>By visiting this page on our website: <a href="/contact" class="text-primary hover:underline">weddingtravelcompany.com/contact</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>